title: Kathie Denosky-One Night, Two Babies
description:
Genres: Romance, Fiction
One Night, Two Babies Kathie DeNosky Heiress Arielle Garnier was pregnant - with twins - and the father-to-be was nowhere in sight - until he barged into her office. Zach Forsythe, billionaire resort owner, was the man she-d had a week-long affair with. Why had Zach lied about his name and left her without a word? Valente-s Baby Maxine Sullivan For Matthew Valente, paternity trumped everything. Never mind that his ex-employee Lana had kept his baby a secret for nearly a year or that he considered her a liar and a thief. Their child would bear the Valente name-and so would she!
